Questions:
Which of the following procedures is considered experimental in the UGLOC study?
A) Standard laparoscopic ovarian cystectomy without ultrasound guidance;
B) Intra-operative ultrasound guidance during laparoscopic ovarian cystectomy;
C) Regular post-operative follow-up with your general practitioner;
D) Accessing medical notes by the research team for data analysis.

Correct answer: B
